Overview
========

**appfoyer** is a tiny command-line Appveyor client.

Usage
=====

* show build history::

      appfoyer https://ci.appveyor.com/project/<user>/<project>/history

  or, for the GitHub repo in current working directory::

      appfoyer .

* show information about the build::

      appfoyer https://ci.appveyor.com/project/<user>/<project>/build/<version>

* show the job log::

      appfoyer https://ci.appveyor.com/project/<user>/<project>/build/<version>/job/<job-id>

You can omit the ``https://ci.appveyor.com/project/`` prefix.

Prerequisites
=============

* Python ≥ 3.3; or ≥ 3.4 on Windows

* colorama_

.. _colorama:
   https://pypi.org/project/colorama/

